<item>
            <title>[LU-15113] test 398g fails with 9 RPCs in flight instead of 8</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15113</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Every once in a great while, some other operation - I can&apos;t tell what - triggers a single write RPC to a different file in test 398g on Gatekeeper testing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This has nothing to do with the test but does cause it to fail occasionally.&#160; An easy solution that isn&apos;t too bad for the test is to add a margin of +1 RPCs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
